<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><b><i>Quote:</i></b><hr> Let me be clear about my position. If you want to say &quot;that's gay&quot; to mean &quot;that's dumb&quot;, fine. But don't expect me to continue to respect you afterwards.<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
